3,"dislike":0,"score":13,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T08:35:51.000Z","msg":"抽水摸人個胸就係朱冠強?"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T08:36:40.000Z","msg":"似係<br />\n隻狗個名都起埋出黎<br />\n又摸人大脾內側<br />\n竟然冇人開post.."},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T10:35:31.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><br />\n大家注意⚠️<br />\n朱冠強趁捉人時抽水</span>"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-20T20:24:26.000Z","msg":"重申七一宣言，設立死線，立即實行雙普選<br />\n<br />\n「勇武派」、「和理非」係角色，唔係派系，理念一致，只係手法不同<br />\n<br />\n唔係仇警，大家一定要清楚知道點解要清算警隊。警暴（濫捕、濫告、不依法規）係暴政一部分，唔全面改革警隊、監警制度，只會令目前同將來爭取雙普選更加舉步維艱<br />\n<br />\n所以，絕對唔需要否認自己係針對警隊，針對警隊就係對準政權。唔通你淨係針對林鄭、唔針對政制，就會有雙普選？<br />\n<br />\n#五大訴求 缺一不可<br />\n#唔撤就罷<br />\n#罷工罷巿罷買罷課<br />\n#我係香港人<br />\n#我參與全港四罷<br />\n#各區集會<br />\n#出核彈麻包袋都唔割蓆<br />\n#直至政府跪低<br />\n#重組警隊 刑事追究 改革監警制度<br />\n#永遠不光顧荃灣北角元朗商戶<br />\n#抵制一切紅媒相關商業活動"},{"pid":"ce66db109dded5fbc4ab660e4540d0251aebebcc","tid":1461591,"uid":254114,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-21T01:33:49.000Z","msg":"Up"},{"pid":"fe1c9f00d8e58800b2dbe13a3a2f69761dfc72c3","tid":1461591,"uid":230911,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-21T01:36:39.000Z","msg":"幫推"},{"pid":"f12da7325fc6d456dc5324507bfa80aed4123004","tid":1461591,"uid":38784,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-21T01:37:49.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"466af4bceaf04fe695f633f00c06ce3ff54afbde","tid":1461591,"uid":268691,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-21T01:53:38.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b3fbf64c844c92373551c62799ce53e87abb990d","tid":1461591,"uid":254114,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-21T04:45:13.000Z","msg":"Never forget"},{"pid":"b4040e0524627bb8c3cbbb53101e2de73ae7faf9","tid":1461591,"uid":52228,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy"